Package: echos
Type: Package
Title: Echo State Networks for Time Series Modeling and Forecasting
Version: 1.0.0
Description: The package provides a comprehensive set of functions and methods 
    for modeling and forecasting univariate time series using Echo State 
    Networks (ESNs). The package features a lightweight implementation that 
    enables fast and fully automatic model training and forecasting using ESNs.
